info.name: The (old) Simpsons API
info.description:
A collection of various API requests to different Simpsons APIs.

See request documentation for more details on each request.

item.name: Characters

variable.description: Required. Valid ID for Simpsons character.

request.description: Returns character based on Character ID.

variable.description: Required. ID of the Simpsons character to fetch.

request.description: Returns a list of characters from The Simpsons sorted by ID.

response.name: Get Simpsons Characters

item.description: Requests that return characters from the simpsons.

request.description: Returns a random Simpsons quote including the author and an image from the show.

response.name: Get Random Simpsons Quote

request.description: Returns a random Simpsons episode including the title, season, episode number, air date, description, and link to view the episode on Disney plus.
